# R&D bootstrap (Mission Control warm-up)

**Target:** This file is the **single** research-and-development center rule with `alwaysApply: true` once the §5.4 parity gate completes. Numbered rules **`10`–`50`** load **on demand** via lane manifests and explicit `Read` steps — not on every dispatch warm-up until the host resolver and frontmatter flip ship (reduce-alwaysapply-governance-load PRD §5.4).

Sedea platform bootstrap and numbered Sedea rules load per **`.sedea/centers/sedea/rules/bootstrap.mdc`** and mission **`laneRules`** — not duplicated here.

---

## Research-and-development center

The **research-and-development** center owns **plan and deliver** delivery process, PR shipping conventions, planning-target resolution, and R&D Mission Control display discipline.

| Tree | Role |
|------|------|
| **`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/`** | Center governance (this file + numbered rules) |
| **`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/`** | Mission **`plan.mdc`**, skills, protocol branches |
| **`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/docs/`** | **`development-process.md`** — NFD cadence, ship chain glossary |

Built-in **`sedea`** center lives at **`.sedea/centers/sedea/`** — see Sedea bootstrap for hosting layout, operations union, and platform spawn protocol.

