|------|------|-----------|
| **10** Plan naming | [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/10_plan-naming-convention.mdc`](10_plan-naming-convention.mdc) | Plan/PR/worktree naming, forbidden-word policy |
| **20** PR shipping | [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/20_efficient-pr-shipping.mdc`](20_efficient-pr-shipping.mdc) | Worktrees, commit/push cadence, ship chain, PR creation gate |
| **30** Planning targets | [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/30_planning-target-resolution.mdc`](30_planning-target-resolution.mdc) | Resolve `.plan.md` targets, snapshot tables, depth-first gates |
| **31** Operations user id | [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/31_operations-user-id.mdc`](31_operations-user-id.mdc) | `operationsUserId`, plans union, `plan-state.mjs --operations-user-id` |
| **40** Maintain rules | [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/40_maintain-rules.mdc`](40_maintain-rules.mdc) | Hosting-repo **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** routing vs center rules |
| **50** Display metadata | [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/50_mission-control-display-metadata-discipline.mdc`](50_mission-control-display-metadata-discipline.mdc) | Child lane display refresh, Squad Leader dispatch scope |

Mission **`plan.mdc`**, **`development-process.md`**, and skill **`SKILL.md`** procedures load per **`laneRules`** and **`skillWarmUp`** — not duplicated here.

